<u><span style="font-size: 35px">ENTRANCES</span></u>
*Standing on an escalator in one of [[Level 833|Level 833's]] airports can rarely send one to this level;
*Rubbing your eyes in an open field far from houses in [[Level 232]] may send one to this level;
*Passing through the unlocked door in [[Level 332]] has a slim chance of leading to this level, among others;
*Jumping into a pit lined with boards in [[Level 6]] can lead to '''Level 500'''.
*Noclipping through a surface shone by sunlight in [[Level 464]] sends one here.
*At [[Level 416]], noclipping through a pathway sends wanderers to this level.
<u><span style="font-size: 35px">EXITS</span></u>
*The interior of certain houses may gradually transition into [[Level 4]] or [[Level 21|Level 21;]]
*Staring into the Core for prolonged periods while near the center can transport one to [[Level 117|Level 117,]] [[Level 140|Level 140,]] [[Level 165|Level 165,]] [[Level 221|Level 221,]] [[Level 499|Level 499,]] or [[Level 989|Level 989.]]
*Dying to Kharthiact exposure may rarely cause one to awake in [[Level 997]].

